---
title: Seasoned Shrimp and Roasted Potatoes with Tomato and Feta Spinach Salad
description: Garlic and shrimp aren't the only stars of this dish. Old Bay-seasoned potatoes and a bright, crisp spinach salad topped with salty feta also shine through. Your taste buds will be singing!
